# Task T-002@20260416T054258Z: Add spatial, reverb, and delay production profiles.

## Acceptance Criteria

- phase profiles define stereo width, near/far depth, reverb size/decay/damping, delay style, and transition-space behavior<br/>- tracker scenes expose spatial intent and reverb/delay sends<br/>- tests verify wide sparse openings, clearer Conversation space, focused Convergence, and long Crystallization tails

**Tier:** T1

